title: Barbara Davis Center for Diabetes Endowed Telehealth Fund
description: To provide support for the telehealth program at the Barbara Davis Center for Diabetes. The fund will provide flexible resources for advancing strategic initiatives, strengthening core offerings, and addressing the telehealth program's greatest needs.
